{"tid":2157371,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港康碼資料勢送中 私隱例不保障","createTime":"2020-08-15T03:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T10:55:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8ad95ba7b46154ba986d36a39058b20a7a27019a","tid":2157371,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:57:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/DDDMAECFQFBXLCN76NCVL6WPTI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2FDDDMAECFQFBXLCN76NCVL6WPTI%2F&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8ZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=96319b27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2FDDDMAECFQFBXLCN76NCVL6WPTI%2F&h=a5bc69be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/DDDMAECFQFBXLCN76NCVL6WPTI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港康碼資料勢送中 私隱例不保障<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2O5imSWlK9bvg6I7u1BSKPncKbA=/1330x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EDMSHBTUPVFBPCZEMNIDSVVT6A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2O5imSWlK9bvg6I7u1BSKPncKbA%3D%2F1330x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEDMSHBTUPVFBPCZEMNIDSVVT6A.jpg&h=1d674a84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■內地健康碼被視為監控民眾行蹤的工具。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】建制派近日要求推港版健康碼，市民憑碼才可出入食肆和商場；政府回應指健康碼只會用於粵港澳三地通關。資訊科技界人士憂慮，健康碼收集的個人資料一旦被送中，將不受本港私隱條例保障，即使被濫用亦無途徑追究。<br />\n<br />\n政府前晚。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原供三地政府過關認證<br />\n<br />\n從事大數據技術分析的IT界選委黃浩華指，重點在有否過度收集DNA等個人資料，同時三地政府會如何使用數據，有否資料儲存期限。他認為健康碼獲三地政府互認，數據庫資料必定送中，但資料出境後便不受《個人資料（私隱）條例》保障，「對方仲要係官方機構，唔係普通私人公司，市民可以點追究？」<br />\n<br />\n香港資訊科技界工會主席鄧卓文亦指內地電腦資訊安全劣績斑斑，曾有內地網軍成員被起底，連銀行戶口資料也曝光，質疑港版健康碼強迫港人「自願」把資料送中，難保安全。民主黨立法會議員黃碧雲批評，內地健康碼已淪為監控市民的程式，質疑保皇黨大力推銷港版健康碼是借疫維穩，進行監控。<br />\n<br />\n《私隱條例》。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"d6c7602ef14aeb6ed171b4c244d4ade97847ef7d","tid":2157371,"uid":57073,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:58:43.000Z","msg":"連回鄉證張相都俾人拎出來起底binc<br />\n你信?"},{"pid":"5f1d33f1df74e37b2bfd7e22cb27e8b0ede11eaf","tid":2157371,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T04:00:55.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n（千祈咪做檢測）一人留DNA，全家十八代奶野。廢老做檢測，後生比人拉。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2142723\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2142723</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"856934c3e51b40a718e6581574e387b1bcd954a0","tid":2157371,"uid":54975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T04:03:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"320548ba0de2b23ffc3aba7078f04ccccba680ac","tid":2157371,"uid":43062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T04:05:37.000Z","msg":"2020仲信政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e05e20b6d479f0b92c9d09b59f2a86f14c6df1","tid":2157371,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T04:06:26.000Z","msg":"廢老：支持健康碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0cde660bc17c94b6a2d44542da275f37937fd26","tid":2157371,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T04:07:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"adfe21ca0ab28231eea3901675b86bb7f396798e","tid":2157371,"uid":161711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:11:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b58202d001c5b42d360cebcd5c77220661162349","tid":2157371,"uid":173002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:13:15.000Z","msg":"暴政：驗武漢病毒抽DNA係國家安全，唔係兩制事務，有權配合強國防疫提供資料。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8e690c526a91d2fd0dd27b597d9a83589cf319","tid":2157371,"uid":253826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:50:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37521b2ff811e9cbc403acd769939b7e70668724","tid":2157371,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T10:55:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}